{"tid":2509912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《災難女孩》MEME迷因圖$50萬美金高價拍出　主角13年後首享NFT收益","createTime":"2021-04-29T19:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T19:46:16.000Z","uid":259777,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2cde2d63848c0ab4329e20bd650920ca70ac723","tid":2509912,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210429/photo/bkn-20210429190006936-0429_00992_001_01p.jpg?20210429231442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20210429%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210429190006936-0429_00992_001_01p.jpg%3F20210429231442&h=dd4f2865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張面露詭譎笑容的女孩照片，16年來被網民改圖惡搞，並廣泛流傳成為迷因圖（meme）。這張名為《災難女孩》（Disaster girl）的照片近日終於為它的女主角、北卡羅萊納州22歲女大學生羅斯（Zoe Roth）帶來財富。<span class=\"red\">她最近把《災難女孩》的原圖放到網上拍賣，成功獲利180個虛擬貨幣以太幣，折合47.3萬美元（約367萬港元）。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">《災難女孩》攝於2005年，當時年僅4歲的羅斯與父親經過一個火災現場，拍下她回頭暗笑的相片。</span>2008年父親參加比賽勝出，照片被上傳網絡，自此成為網民萬能key。然而羅斯一家從沒有因此獲得一分一毫利益，直至近日他們獲出售表情貼圖的專家建議，2星期前把相片原圖放到網上公開拍賣，才得知這相片能賣得這價錢。<br />\n<br />\n高價拍下《災難女孩》原圖的，是一位名「3FMusic」的網民。由於他以以太幣結算，根據該種「非同質化代幣」（NFT）虛擬貨幣的演算法，羅斯以後仍可以從每次轉售抽取10%的版稅。羅斯接受傳媒訪問時指出：「成功出售相片原圖，代表我們仍對它有一定的控制權」。<br />\n<br />\n迷因圖在網上為數不少，例如著名的《暴躁貓》（Grumpy Cat），雖然真身貓貓早在2019年已去世，但迷因圖原圖卻在NFT市場以逾10萬美元佳績拍出。"},{"pid":"6b42c736da775e87b6aa95b7c781aa406a77d29d","tid":2509912,"uid":271397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:18:46.000Z","msg":"呢個價真係超值<br />\n一定有得炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33afcafb8b7974f27fe6630e5d9e4052f655de8","tid":2509912,"uid":259777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:20:18.000Z","msg":"呢篇文冇講<br />\n其實佢後面果場火係消防員特登放，然後開放俾果個區嘅小朋友體驗做消防員救火<br />\n所以其實場火根本唔係災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e43f3c8b1cfbecee2d4b458ef7d01cee8c918ae","tid":2509912,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"唔好搵佢大個個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb65961369789789e04df5dfdf64da4d519d403","tid":2509912,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:22:38.000Z","msg":"極壞之凱霆 又會拍賣到幾錢？"},{"pid":"185969a85ad0c1aea5294e7be67303fd57963ece","tid":2509912,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:26:48.000Z","msg":"呢張呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/ff/SuccessKid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Ff%2Fff%2FSuccessKid.jpg&h=fc15a9f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38d9dbd4b4377e7be4e5e972fbf8c3c8b43afaeb","tid":2509912,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:29:10.000Z","msg":"唔知Pepe賣到幾多<br />\n搵人畫之後捐錢都好"},{"pid":"7230a9671bb1c35667d980e35fbf23f55a24be38","tid":2509912,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e43f3c8b1cfbecee2d4b458ef7d01cee8c918ae","tid":2509912,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"唔好搵佢大個個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.gulte.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Di-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gulte.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2FDi-1024x576.jpg&h=584030f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c29d5490dff99eb4b1506a849e223c995055e7f0","tid":2509912,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38d9dbd4b4377e7be4e5e972fbf8c3c8b43afaeb","tid":2509912,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:29:10.000Z","msg":"唔知Pepe賣到幾多<br />\n搵人畫之後捐錢都好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T19:46:16.000Z","msg":"個市已經極多pepe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.